<l>cuṭṭumuta lukara maṉṉoṭu civaṇi</l>
<l>yoṭṭiya meyyoḻit tukaraṅ keṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Words which] begin with a demonstrative<note
              place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">cuṭṭumutal.</foreign></note></l>
<l>[and end in] the sound <foreign xml:lang="ta">u</foreign> take <foreign xml:lang="ta">aṉ</foreign></l>
<l>[before the case-marker], remove (or transform ?)</l>
<l>the appropriate consonant and lose the <foreign xml:lang="ta">u.</foreign><note
              place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">at-aṉ-ai, it-aṉ-oṭu.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
